<ab facs="#facs_215_r1l19">ſınd . etc . Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vormals </ab>
