<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lugweig<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Payern und
